reviewText: Everything I knew it would be.

The video quality is excellent as is the sound. However, I just noticed the discs are labeled "fourth" season even through they are third season. This is not problematic as the case is labeled properly. However, if yours come the same way I thought you might appreciate knowing. I bought the First-Fourth seasons and have been very pleased with the quality.
Dvds are clear and in excellent condition. Well worth being digitally remastered and very good packaging from seller.
Loved this show as a kid this show got me into scuba diving even done one shark dive.
completes the set. easy watching and entertaining when theres nothing good to watch on tv.
The digitally remaster on this set was great. I enjoyed watching it more than the televised episodes. Best of all, no commercials! :)
Arrived on time, nice packaging, excellent quality video. 26 minutes of uninterrupted joy per episode.

This series is really hitting it's stride in season 3. The episodes are as good as the prior 2 seasons and as far as I know there is nothing out there like it. Good quality picture on my large screen TV also. It is black and white, but the stories are absorbing so I barely notice that.
